description:
gesserit presents:

   A Hitlist Fills Torrent ( <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9591710" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9591710</a>  ):

      A Collection of Traditionally Scanned releases:




         Space Race 001-002 (1993-1994) (both c2c) (ArtNet-DCP)




         So far, all HiFis in this branch have been Big-Two superhero titles. This
         one is a bit different: Based on the name and a quick look, it seems to be
         sci-fi, and the artwork is black-and-white and manga-style. The last page

         search results and the comicbookdb entry, the series was then discontinued.
